name: Frida Punk 016 - Pained to paint
description: Fun fact: Frida used her art to depict her illnesses and injuries. Her piece "Broken Column" shows her shattered spine appearing like an earthquake fissure. Another piece, "Without Hope", depicts a time when Frida completely lost her appetite, and so her Doctor prescribed her to be force fed a fattening purée every 2 hours.
